EB01-EB01-001 normal.name: Kouzuki Oden
EB01-EB01-001 normal.description:
All of your [Land of Wano] type Character cards without a Counter have a +1000 Counter, according to the rules.
[DON!! x1] [When Attacking] If you have a [Land of Wano] type Character with a cost of 5 or more, this Leader gains +1000 power until the start of your next turn.

EB01-EB01-001 foil.name: Kouzuki Oden (Alternate Art)
EB01-EB01-001 foil.description:
All of your [Land of Wano] type Character cards without a Counter have a +1000 Counter, according to the rules.
[DON!! x1] [When Attacking] If you have a [Land of Wano] type Character with a cost of 5 or more, this Leader gains +1000 power until the start of your next turn.

EB01-EB01-002 foil.name: Izo
EB01-EB01-002 foil.description:
[On Play] Give up to 1 rested DON!! card to your Leader or 1 of your Characters.
[On Your Opponent's Attack] [Once Per Turn] You may trash 1 card from your hand: If your Leader has the [Land of Wano] or [Whitebeard Pirates] type, give up to 1 of your opponent's Leader or Character cards -2000 power during this turn.

EB01-EB01-006 foil.description:

EB01-EB01-007 normal.name: Yamato
EB01-EB01-007 normal.description: [Activate:Main] [Once Per Turn] Give up to 1 rested DON!! card to your Leader or 1 of your Characters.

EB01-EB01-008 foil.name: LittleOars Jr.
EB01-EB01-008 foil.description: [Once Per Turn] If this Character would be K.O.'d by an effect, you may trash 1 Event or Stage card from your hand instead.

EB01-EB01-009 normal.name: Just Shut Up and Come with Us!!!!
EB01-EB01-009 normal.description: [Counter] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck and play up to 1 [Animal] type Character card with a cost of 3 or less. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

EB01-EB01-010 foil.name: There's No Way You Could Defeat Me!!
EB01-EB01-010 foil.description:

[Trigger] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 5000 base power or less.

EB01-EB01-011 normal.description: [Activate:Main] You may rest this card and place 1 of your Characters with 1000 base power at the bottom of your deck: Draw 1 card.

EB01-EB01-012 foil.name: Cavendish
EB01-EB01-012 foil.description: [On Play]/[When Attacking] If your Leader has the [Supernovas] type and you have no other [Cavendish] Characters, set up to 2 of your DON!! cards as active.

Then, look at 3 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 [Donquixote Pirates] type Character card and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

EB01-EB01-027 foil.name: Mr. 1 (Daz.Bonez)

[Trigger] Return up to 1 Character with a cost of 3 or less to the bottom of the owner's deck.

EB01-EB01-029 normal.description:

[Trigger] Return up to 1 Character with a cost of 8 or less to the owner's hand.

EB01-EB01-034 foil.name: Ms. Wednesday

[Trigger] DON!! -1: Draw 2 cards.

EB01-EB01-039 foil.name: Conquerer of Three Worlds Ragnaraku
